{
  "id": "69eb2b09c64d30ad6e65be82",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:いじりはどこまで許されるのか",
  "created": 1777019679,
  "updated": 1777019714,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69eb2b09c64d30ad6e65be82",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:いじりはどこまで許されるのか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019679,
      "updated": 1777019679
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b1f0000000000f5dbd7",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019679,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbd8",
      "text": "「はいどーもー、今日のゆるトークテーマは『[いじりはどこまで許されるのか]』でーす！いやこれさ、クラスでもあるあるじゃん？“それいじり？それただのディスでは？”みたいなやつ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019693
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbd9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbda",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbdb",
      "text": "「定義から整理しよう。いじりは“軽いユーモアを伴う対人コミュニケーション”。ただし、受け手の主観的快・不快が評価軸になる。ここがポイント」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbdc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbdd",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbde",
      "text": "「出た、りかの辞書タイム。つまり“相手が笑ってたらセーフ、ムッとしたらアウト”ってことね？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbdf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbe0",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbe1",
      "text": "「概ねそう。ただし“その場では笑っていても内心は不快”というケースもある。表情だけで判断するのは精度が低い」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbe2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbe3",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbe4",
      "text": "「たしかに……人は時に、場の空気に合わせて微笑んでしまうこともございますね。（微笑）その笑みが、必ずしも心の安らぎを意味するとは限らないのが、少し切ないところです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbe5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbe6",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbe7",
      "text": "「うわぁ、なんか文学的に重くなった…！でもわかるわ。“とりま笑っとこ”みたいなやつあるもんね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbe8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbe9",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbea",
      "text": "「ゆえに、許容範囲は“関係性・文脈・頻度”の3変数で決まると考えられる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbeb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbec",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbed",
      "text": "「変数とか言い出したよこの人。ゲームのステータスみたいに言うな」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbef",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbf0",
      "text": "「シンプルに言うとこうだ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbf1",
      "text": " 1. 関係性：信頼があるか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbf2",
      "text": " 2. 文脈：場の空気が安全か",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbf3",
      "text": " 3. 頻度：やりすぎていないか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbf4",
      "text": "」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbf5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbf6",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbf7",
      "text": "「その三つが調和しているとき、言葉は軽やかな羽のように相手に届くのでしょうね。けれど、どれかが欠けると……少し鋭い棘になってしまうのかもしれません」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbf8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbf9",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbfa",
      "text": "「あや、それ詩集出せるよ。タイトル『いじりの棘』でどう？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbfb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbfc",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbfd",
      "text": "「それは少し刺激が強い題名かもしれませんね……（笑う）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbfe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dbff",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc00",
      "text": "「実例を出そう。“背が低いね”という発言。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc01",
      "text": " 親友同士で軽く言う→ユーモア",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc02",
      "text": " 初対面で言う→リスクが高い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc03",
      "text": " 繰り返し言う→負荷が蓄積",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc04",
      "text": "こういうモデルになる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc05",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc06",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc07",
      "text": "「なるほどねー。親友でも毎日“チビチビ”言われたら、さすがにHP削られるわ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc08",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc09",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc0a",
      "text": "「HPという表現は適切だ。心理的耐久値と考えればいい」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc0b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc0c",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc0d",
      "text": "「言葉は見えないものですが、確かに心に触れて、少しずつ影響を残しますものね。だからこそ、やさしく扱いたいものです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc0e",
      "text": "ふーこ「じゃあさ、結論どうする？“全部ダメ！”ってわけでもないし、“何でもOK！”でもないし」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc0f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc10",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc11",
      "text": "「結論：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc12",
      "text": "“相手が安心して笑える範囲で、かつ継続的に確認されるものだけが許容されるいじり”」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc13",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc14",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc15",
      "text": "「うん、長い。3行で」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc16",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc17",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc18",
      "text": "「短縮する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc19",
      "text": " 相手がOKか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc1a",
      "text": " 場がOKか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc1b",
      "text": " やりすぎてないか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc1c",
      "text": "」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc1d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc1e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc1f",
      "text": "「とてもわかりやすくなりましたね（微笑）まるで道しるべのようです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc20",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc21",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc22",
      "text": "「つまり“空気読んで、ほどほどに、ちゃんと相手見ろ”ってことね。はい解散！……って雑すぎるか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc23",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc24",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc25",
      "text": "「要約としては適切だ。だが“観察と配慮”も追加したい」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc26",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc27",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc28",
      "text": "「うわ、ラスボスみたいな条件増えた」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc29",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc2a",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc2b",
      "text": "「けれど、そのひと手間が、誰かの心を守るのかもしれませんね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc2c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc2d",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc2e",
      "text": "「……よし、じゃあ今日のまとめ！“いじりはスキル制。初心者は無理するな！”」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc2f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc30",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc31",
      "text": "「それは一理ある」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc32",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc33",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
    },
    {
      "id": "69eb2b200000000000f5dc34",
      "text": "「ええ、優しさという基礎があってこそ、成り立つものですものね（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1777019680,
      "updated": 1777019680
